=== OJS CMS Plugin\
=== Version: 1.0\
=== Release date: April 1, 2007\
=== Author: Juan Pablo Alperin <juan@geeky.net>\
================================\
\
About\
-----\
This plugin for OJS 2 provides a Simple CMS that allows for the creation and maintenance of static content pages.\
\
License\
